Property analyzer: rental insights, STR estimates, API integrations, UI polish

Features:
- Add RentalInsights component with Airbnb potential, market snapshot, demand indicators
- Integrate RentCast API for rental comps and AVM rent estimates
- Integrate AirDNA API for short-term rental market data
- Add algorithmic STR estimation service as fallback
- Add STREstimate type to shared-types
- Add shareable analysis URLs (/analysis/:id) with auto-load from URL
- Make history cards clickable to navigate to saved analyses

UI/UX improvements:
- Recharts bar chart for rent comparison (replaces CSS bars)
- Sortable, paginated comps table with click-to-highlight
- Compact foreclosure list with list/map toggle and pagination
- Property photo in header card (with empty state)
- Tax savings inlined into cash flow card
- Bottom grid layout for foreclosures + loan calculator
- 2-column loan calculator sliders
- TermExplainer info icons on all rental insights sections (13 new terms)
- Signal badges (Good/Fair/Caution) on demand indicators
- External link icon column in comps table (row click = select, icon = open)

Data quality and performance:
- Filter Xome market stats with invalid dollar values
- Increase cache TTLs: Zillow 24h, RentCast 24h, AirDNA 24h, Xome listings 4h, trends 7d
- Extract property photos from Zillow response
- Remove API integration references from disclaimer
